CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 19, reads: "8. TitMainTitle: Dick Kramer, and Leonard Komoroski helping customer Carrie Moore in the Lowther Builders and Greater Pittsburgh Lumber and Supply Company booth, at the Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in the Syria Mosque
